1. \k{User Setup Window}
   1.2 \k{View Button^^View ButtonUS}
       1.2.3 Reserved

The Reserved menu option lets you view icons representing reserved
accounts (accounts defined by the UNIX system). These accounts are reserved for
special use by UNIX SVR4.2. Do not delete any reserved accounts.

When you select the Reserved menu option, reserved account icons are
displayed in the User Setup window.
^2^Account Button=Account ButtonUS
